{
  "stem": "2804.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because when we went in and we started to-- well, word spread so fast, the Americanas have come, because they had seen the soldiers before.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when we went in, you know, that they knew that it was the Americans coming to save them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Didn't have time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's always been in back of my mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There are certain movies that I will not see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did go-- in 1969, I took a trip to Israel for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And like Yad Vashem, I did not go in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were certain places I did not go into.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We went into-- two weeks in Israel, then we went into Italy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we went up to Amsterdam and London.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in Amsterdam, they-- I went with the American Jewish Congress, which was a beautiful trip.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They stopped at Anne Frank, and everybody went up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- I stayed on the bus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I did not go up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I know of.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had taken-- I had a camera, and I had taken pictures.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think before-- the soldiers that came in that liberated the camp to-- they-- they had film, because I have it on a film called And it shows going into-- the people first going into Dachau.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they it all film-- on film.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They have pictures of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every soldier you talked to, when they went into a camp they did not know what to expect.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No way.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not really, because what we had, and then the army did, as I said-- they supplied us with the beds and the-- you know, when we cleaned out the barracks where the German soldiers stayed.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And supplies came in to help.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
